[
  {
    "startTime": 6.5,
    "endTime": 9.120000000000001,
    "text": "Aww, did a wittle puppy dog get stuck in here again?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.02,
    "endTime": 11.08,
    "text": "Son of a biscuit!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.98,
    "endTime": 16.96,
    "text": "Oh! Is everything okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.28,
    "endTime": 18.880000000000003,
    "text": "I think there's a critter in my trash can!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.82,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "You don't say!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 26.2,
    "text": "I just love wild animals!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.2,
    "endTime": 27.72,
    "text": "Well, this one scared the bejesus out of me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.72,
    "endTime": 29.72,
    "text": "Oh, it's probably frightened!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.64,
    "endTime": 31.14,
    "text": "Wait--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.0,
    "endTime": 34.56,
    "text": "Oh! It's a possum!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.56,
    "endTime": 35.5,
    "text": "It looks pretty grumpy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.5,
    "endTime": 37.26,
    "text": "Oh, I've seen worse!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.62,
    "endTime": 39.519,
    "text": "Well, I guess I'll call animal control--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.74,
    "endTime": 52.38,
    "text": "Oh! It got out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.8,
    "endTime": 56.879,
    "text": "There's no need to be afraid! Our little friend was just lost!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.36,
    "endTime": 58.26,
    "text": "So do we let him loose?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.54,
    "endTime": 63.44,
    "text": "Oh no silly! Now he comes home to live with me and my 43 other animals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.019,
    "endTime": 65.899,
    "text": "Oh, and my seven coal miner roommates."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.88,
    "endTime": 67.38,
    "text": "Boop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.38,
    "endTime": 68.02,
    "text": "Do what now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.02,
    "endTime": 69.78,
    "text": "Let's get you all cleaned up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.8,
    "endTime": 73.7,
    "text": "You probably shouldn't have told me any of that! I... I'm the president of the HOA!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.72,
    "endTime": 74.36,
    "text": "Buh-bye!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.46,
    "endTime": 76.759,
    "text": "That's way too many animals!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.58,
    "endTime": 85.94,
    "text": "Well, found the problem, but, uh, it ain't good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.4,
    "endTime": 89.22,
    "text": "I knew it. Every dadgum July this thing breaks down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.4,
    "endTime": 91.66000000000001,
    "text": "Evaporator coil this time. The whole thing is shot!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.3,
    "endTime": 93.24,
    "text": "What's that gonna set me back?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.52,
    "endTime": 96.92,
    "text": "Full replacement, parts and labor... you're looking at a couple thousand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.1,
    "endTime": 97.899,
    "text": "Are you serious??"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.22,
    "endTime": 99.98,
    "text": "There is one other option."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.32,
    "endTime": 102.839,
    "text": "Is it cheaper, cause, I could probably just fix it myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.06,
    "endTime": 104.54,
    "text": "Well I'd talk to her first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.66,
    "endTime": 110.979,
    "text": "Let it go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.14,
    "endTime": 112.78,
    "text": "Let it go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.78,
    "endTime": 113.8,
    "text": "I think she's talking to you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.24,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "Put the screwdriver down!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.58,
    "text": "You... you're not burning up in that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.72,
    "endTime": 124.66,
    "text": "Oh, the heat never bothered me anyway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.3,
    "endTime": 126.92,
    "text": "It's really the humidity that will get you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.92,
    "endTime": 128.42000000000002,
    "text": "So, what do we have here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.12,
    "endTime": 131.08,
    "text": "-Total evap coil failure? -Yup."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.08,
    "endTime": 132.68,
    "text": "-How's the condenser? -Brand new."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.68,
    "endTime": 133.82,
    "text": "-Freon? -Fully charged."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.52,
    "endTime": 138.20000000000002,
    "text": "Well, I can ice blast this for you for about fifty bucks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.2,
    "endTime": 139.57899999999998,
    "text": "That'll hold you over for a while."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.02,
    "endTime": 140.52,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.2,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "You serious?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 142.5,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 144.64,
    "text": "There might be a side effect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 146.02,
    "text": "Talking snowman."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.5,
    "endTime": 147.96,
    "text": "But he dances and sings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.66,
    "endTime": 150.04,
    "text": "But the house will stay cool?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.4,
    "endTime": 151.78,
    "text": "Below freezing till October."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.86,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "All right, let's do it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 156.0,
    "text": "Step back!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.86,
    "endTime": 163.10000000000002,
    "text": "Look at this stuff!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.32,
    "endTime": 163.959,
    "text": "Isn't it neat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.3,
    "endTime": 165.38000000000002,
    "text": "Lord! You scared me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.9,
    "endTime": 167.98000000000002,
    "text": "Sorry! I just got my voice back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.74,
    "endTime": 170.54000000000002,
    "text": "Is this for sale?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.54,
    "endTime": 172.14,
    "text": "Yeah. It's all for sale."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.3,
    "endTime": 174.84,
    "text": "But you should've come earlier, there was a lot better stuff here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.06,
    "endTime": 176.56,
    "text": "This looks dangerous!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.54,
    "endTime": 181.28,
    "text": "I have, on occasion, used it as a weapon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.86,
    "endTime": 185.96,
    "text": "I've tried everything to get that stain out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.2,
    "endTime": 187.82,
    "text": "It's so beautiful!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.68,
    "endTime": 189.84,
    "text": "You like the Salt Life?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.68,
    "endTime": 192.8,
    "text": "Once upon a time, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.24,
    "endTime": 193.84,
    "text": "I understand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.38,
    "endTime": 195.66,
    "text": "I'm from Pascagoula."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.92,
    "endTime": 197.79999999999998,
    "text": "Is that a thingamabob?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.8,
    "endTime": 198.94,
    "text": "That doohickey?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.38,
    "endTime": 200.38,
    "text": "Yeah. It's broken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.64,
    "endTime": 202.779,
    "text": "If you push it hard enough and turn it to the right it sometimes..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.92,
    "endTime": 203.95899999999997,
    "text": "I'll take it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.96,
    "endTime": 205.5,
    "text": "I'll take all of it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.5,
    "endTime": 208.46,
    "text": "This leftover junk?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.88,
    "endTime": 210.96,
    "text": "Now my collection's complete!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.66,
    "endTime": 212.46,
    "text": "Collection?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.1,
    "endTime": 213.6,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.1,
    "endTime": 215.299,
    "text": "You're a hoarder."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.98,
    "endTime": 217.42,
    "text": "All right. Well, that's none of my business."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.8,
    "endTime": 219.12,
    "text": "Twenty dollars sound good?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.74,
    "endTime": 231.88,
    "text": "Did she pay me?"
  }
]